OL,3,CCrimes against women 'being ignored'
OL,4,Cas key statistic excludes rape
OL,6,FCrimes against women are "simply being
OL,7,Fignored" by the government, Labour has
OL,8,Fclaimed, after it was revealed a key
OL,9,Fcrime statistic often quoted by
OL,10,Fministers does not include instances
OL,11,Fof rape or other sexual offences.
OL,13,FShadow Home Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,14,Fsaid she is "extremely concerned about
OL,15,Fthe missing information and analysis
OL,16,Fon what's happening about crimes
OL,17,Fagainst women", following a revelation
OL,18,Fabout the way the Office for National
OL,19,FStatistics (ONS) gathers certain
OL,20,Ffigures.
