OL,3,CCrimes against women 'being ignored'
OL,4,Cas key statistic excludes rape
OL,6,FMinisters have often boasted about a
OL,7,Fhalving of "total" crime since the
OL,8,FConservatives took power in 2010 but
OL,9,Fthe ONS does not include many sexual
OL,10,Foffences when calculating that measure.
OL,12,FIt comes after separate figures
OL,13,Freleased by the suggested more victims
OL,14,Fthan ever before are coming forward
OL,15,Ffor support.
OL,17,FWhy rape and sexual offences aren't
OL,18,Fincluded in the UK's 'total' crime
OL,19,Ffigure
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
