OL,6,FHelen Ross, who works in the Centre
OL,7,Ffor Crime and Justice at ONS,
OL,8,Fexplained why.
OL,10,F"Collecting survey data on sexual
OL,11,Foffences, such as rape and unwanted
OL,12,Fsexual touching, as well as domestic
OL,13,Fabuse, stalking and harassment can be
OL,14,Fespecially challenging.
