OL,6,FMinisters wrongly claim Tories have
OL,7,Fhalved crime since 2010
OL,9,FMs Ross said broad assessments on the
OL,10,Flong term trends of all crime "should
OL,11,Fbe made with caution" for that reason,
OL,12,Fbut that has not stopped the likes of
OL,13,FRishi Sunak, Suella Braverman and
OL,14,Fother Conservatives from claiming to
OL,15,Fhave halved crime.
OL,17,FLast year the prime minister said in
OL,18,Fthe Commons that "our record is clear.
OL,19,FWe have halved crime since 2010".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/13
