OL,6,FMs Braverman, who was formerly the
OL,7,Fhome secretary, also claimed in the
OL,8,FCommons that "overall crime, excluding
OL,9,Fcrime, is down by 50%".
OL,11,FBut Labour's shadow home secretary
OL,12,Fsaid "there's real concern" that "some
OL,13,Fof the most serious crimes that the
OL,14,Fcountry faces" are not being
OL,15,Facknowledged.
