OL,6,F"Labour has set a plan to halve
OL,7,Fviolence against women and girls but
OL,8,Fthat means we need the information, we
OL,9,Fneed the analysis and they need to be
OL,10,Fvisible - we can't have these crimes
OL,11,Fsimply being ignored," Ms Cooper said.
OL,13,FShe said her party would carry out an
OL,14,F"urgent review of the way information
OL,15,Fis gathered because these crimes need
OL,16,Fto be visible".
