OL,6,FMore victims of domestic violence
OL,7,Fsought support than ever before last
OL,8,Fyear, the National Centre for Domestic
OL,9,FAbuse and Violence (NCDV) revealed on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FIts figures showed 100,318 victims of
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse were referred to the
OL,14,Forganisation in 2023, up from 95,905
OL,15,Fin the previous year.
