OL,6,FThe group, which provides free
OL,7,Femergency injunctions for abuse
OL,8,Fsurvivors, said the number of women
OL,9,Fseeking help has risen more than
OL,10,Ffourfold in 10 years - jumping from
OL,11,F23,841 in 2013.
