OL,6,FThe NCDV receives around 60% of
OL,7,Freferrals from police and the rest
OL,8,Ffrom domestic abuse organisations and
OL,9,Fother services. Men are also victims
OL,10,Fof domestic abuse but the vast
OL,11,Fmajority (89.%) referred to the
OL,12,Forganisation are women.
OL,14,FSharon Bryan, head of partnerships at
OL,15,Fthe NCDV, said the number of domestic
OL,16,Fviolence reports it receives are "just
OL,17,Fthe tip of the iceberg".
