OL,6,FShe : "It is terrifying to consider
OL,7,Fthat this may mean 100,318 people
OL,8,Fsitting at home waiting for the key to
OL,9,Fturn in the lock, not knowing what the
OL,10,Fevening holds for them, let alone the
OL,11,Ffuture. 100,318 people walking on
OL,12,Feggshells.
OL,14,F"100,318 people who need protection
OL,15,Ffrom their abuser. All of these people
OL,16,Fare in potentially life threatening
OL,17,Fsituations, and this number is just
OL,18,Fthe tip of the iceberg."
